---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="TopNice privacy policy. Learn how we handle your data."
  lang="en"
>
  <section class="page-content">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: June 2026</p>
    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>TopNice does not require user registration. We do not collect personal information such as names or email addresses unless you voluntarily subscribe to our newsletter.</p>
    <p>We use <strong>Google Analytics</strong> to collect anonymous usage data including page views, traffic sources, and device information. This data helps us improve the website experience.</p>
    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use essential cookies for website functionality and analytics cookies via Google Analytics. You can disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>
    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>Our website links to third-party platforms (Kickstarter, Indiegogo). We are not responsible for their privacy practices. We also use Google AdSense for advertising, which may use cookies to serve personalized ads.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For privacy-related inquiries, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@topnice.com">hello@topnice.com</a>.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 120px 48px 80px;
  }
  .page-content h1 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }
  .page-content h2 {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #0f172a;
    margin-top: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .page-content p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .page-content a {
    color: #f97316;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-content { padding: 100px 20px 60px; }
    .page-content h1 { font-size: 28px; }
  }
</style>
